Package: dcifer
Type: Package
Title: Genetic Relatedness Between Polyclonal Infections
Version: 1.0.0
Author@R: 
    person("Inna", "Gerlovina", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "innager@berkeley.edu", 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7772-7473"))
Description: Dcifer (Distance for complex infections: fast estimation of 
    relatedness) is an IBD-based method to calculate genetic relatedness 
    between polyclonal infections from biallelic and multiallelic data. 
    The package includes functions that format and preprocess the data,
    implement the method, and visualize the results.  
    Gerlovina et al. (2022) <doi:10.1101/2022.04.14.488406>.
